  "body": "What if I'll say that you can show scroll progress in your page? Today I'll explain how to create this awesome thing. So, let's create our scrollbar component and name it, for example **_scrollbar.vue._**\n\nAt first, we need some markup\n\n```html\n<template>\n```html\n\n```html\n\t<div class=\"progress\">\n```\n\n```\n\t  <div class=\"progress-container\">\n```\n\n```\n\t    <div class=\"progress-bar\" ref=\"bar\"></div>\n```\n\n```\n\t  </div> \n```\n\n```\n\t</div>\n```\n\n```\n</template>\n```\n\nThen add some styles,\n\n```\n<style lang='scss'>\n```\n\n```\n\t/* Styles for parent block */\n```\n\n```\n\t.progress {\n```\n\n```\n\t    position: fixed;\n```\n\n```\n\t    top: 0;\n```\n\n```\n\t    left: 100px;\n```\n\n```\n\n```\n\n```\n\t    z-index: 1;\n```\n\n```\n\t    width: 100%;\n```\n\n```\n\t    height: 3px;\n```\n\n```\n\t    border-radius: 0px;\n```\n\n```\n\t}\n```\n\n```\n\n```\n\n```\n\t/* Progress bar container */\n```\n\n```\n\t.progress-container {\n```\n\n```\n\t  width: 100%;\n```\n\n```\n\t  height: 3px;\n```\n\n```\n\t  background: #ccc;\n```\n\n```\n\t}\n```\n\n```\n\t/* Progress bar */\n```\n\n```\n\t.progress-bar {\n```\n\n```\n\t  height: 3px;\n```\n\n```\n\t  background: $accent;\n```\n\n```\n\t  width: 0%;\n```\n\n```\n\t}\n```\n\n```\n</style>\n```\n\nAnd finally, our javascript code:\n\n```\n<script>\n```\n\n```\n\texport default {\n```\n\n```\n\t\tname: 'ScrollBar',\n```\n\n```\n\t\tmethods: {\n```\n\n```\n\t\t    handleScroll () {\n```\n\n```\n\t\t    \tlet winScroll = document.body.scrollTop || document.documentElement.scrollTop;\n```\n\n```\n\t      \t\tlet height = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - document.documentElement.clientHeight;\n```\n\n```\n\t      \t\tlet scrolled = (winScroll / height) * 100;\n```\n\n```\n\n```\n\n```\n\t      \t\tthis.$refs.bar.style.width = scrolled + \"%\";\n```\n\n```\n\t\t    }\n```\n\n```\n\t\t},\n```\n\n```\n\t\tcreated () {\n```\n\n```\n\t\t\twindow.addEventListener('scroll', this.handleScroll);\n```\n\n```\n\t\t},\n```\n\n```\n\t  \tdestroyed () {\n```\n\n```\n                        window.removeEventListener('scroll', this.handleScroll);\n```\n\n```\n\t  \t}\n```\n\n```\n\t}\n```\n\n```\n</script>\n```"
